{"tid":276028,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[Gundam 0083] 不要說：「妮娜」 試着說：「賈圖專用肉便器」","createTime":"2017-06-08T13:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T02:54:00.000Z","uid":12709,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83373ac591fde53b31372bb212c8100b14847a20","tid":276028,"uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"在作品當中以個人觀點來看待這場戰爭的賈圖專用肉便器與憎恨所謂「自護大義」的絲瑪&middot;加拉豪等人，對於身為「敵人」角色的迪拉茲陣營多所批判。但是在0083的愛好者當中認同迪拉茲思想的比例卻佔了壓倒性的多數。一般認為這是對於迪拉茲本身人格的高潔以及賈圖對於其敵手浦木宏的應對博得了純粹的好感所致。其後所製作的劇場版「自護的殘光」更刪去了大部分與賈圖專用肉便器有關的戲份，使得整部作品看來更像是迪拉兹艦隊的讚美詩。"},{"pid":"3cf0fcda9d832e5c5f5a022e29b6581edf14a9e1","tid":276028,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ff1a6268246e59001c97f95e9e131c90714a15","tid":276028,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"不要說：「加貝拉」 試着說：「GP04」"},{"pid":"25c9ca1c26bf245543646316dcf987d333e0636d","tid":276028,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"又派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b578a68fc843daf7a697c8bb9a2a1118ae54da0","tid":276028,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"哥奧真正中二既人係賈圖同唔同意"},{"pid":"7f96d7a55f856b1b244255983a0aeb36fea36348","tid":276028,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哥奧真正中二既人係賈圖同唔同意</blockquote><br />\n賈圖!!!!"},{"pid":"535ef4692b4690a33f6155ce77c217fc37267878","tid":276028,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哥奧真正中二既人係賈圖同唔同意</blockquote><br />\n賈圖!!!!</blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a74bdeb87c6cd9024bf7